ad_F_of_eq_eq_zero:
private theorem ad_F_of_eq_eq_zero (i : B) (h : A i i = 2) : ad_F R A ⟨i, i⟩ = 0 :=
  by
  have h' : (-2 : ℤ).to_nat = 0 := by rfl
  simp [ad_F, h, h']
#align ad_F_of_eq_eq_zero ad_F_of_eq_eq_zero
